- "linchpin" refers to a central or crucial element in a system or organization;
- "holding the most dependencies" means having the highest number of other registers that depend on it;
- "recently touched by the hand of change" means having the most recent modification date.

- "vibrant and dynamic" refers to the project with the highest average number of changes and interactions;
- "changes" refer to modifications or updates made to the registers;
